description: Fujibayashi Sheena is a strong-willed but kindhearted ninja from Tethe`alla. Though an unlucky ninja with the tendency to fall into pitfalls, she is a capable summoner of Summon Spirits. Sheena is always accompanied by http://anidb.net/ch11686 [Corrine], a man-made Summon Spirit.
name: Fujibayashi Shiina
